        <q>Page 2, line 16, at end insert&#x2014;</q>
        <q>("( ) Arrangements under this paragraph shall be co-ordinated with provisions in the <a href="/acts/learning-and-skills-act-2000">Learning and Skills Act 2000</a> for personal advisers for young people. "").</q>
