          <p class='first-para'>
            I think that the Title of the Bill should be changed. We have been talking all evening about young people. I hope that the Minister
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_66gc' title='Col. 66GC &mdash; HL Deb 10 February 2000 vol 609 c66GC' name='column_66gc' href='#column_66gc' rel='bookmark'>66GC</a>
            will take it away with him and look at it because "Children and Young People (Leaving Care) Bill" sounds far more appropriate.
          </p>
